root: ^Hey there, gorgeous! Are you a magician?
^Because whenever I look at you, everyone else disappears!
^Hey, I'm just trying to keep things magical around here!
^But seriously, you must be a parking ticket, because you've got 'FINE' written all over you!
^Hey, when you're in the presence of someone as stunning as you, you gotta pull out all the stops!
^What do you say we grab a coffee sometime and continue this delightful banter?
